# ClaimApp — this file is intentionally empty in the public repo.
#
# NOTE: the deployed GitHub Pages site has NO .env support.
# All keys are entered in the browser UI, stay in memory only, and
# are wiped on refresh.
#
# This file exists only to document that fact and to ensure that anyone
# forking the repo sees `.env*` patterns in .gitignore and does not
# accidentally commit a real key.
#
# DO NOT add private keys, mnemonics, or secrets here.
